    {
      "id": "PopularPost315906",
      "post_content": "To some of the people who don't understand the appeal: It's important to understand that when this card came out, graveyard-recursion and reusable instants or sorceries were almost unheard of. The entire buyback mechanic was basically based on this card (and a few other things, like [Death Spark](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Death Spark).)  \n  \nIt's a bit obsolete now, yeah; like a lot of new mechanics, they overcosted it. 8 mana for 3 damage a turn was a bit much even at the time. But it was a very important card in its day, not so much because of its raw power but because it was doing something that people hadn't really seen before and opened up new areas of design as a result.  \n  \n(The fact that it was really fun to use in casual didn't hurt, of course.)",
      "posted_by": "Aquillion",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost315906\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">To some of the people who don't understand the appeal:  It's important to understand that when this card came out, graveyard-recursion and reusable instants or sorceries were almost unheard of.  The entire buyback mechanic was basically based on this card (and a few other things, like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Death Spark\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Death Spark\">Death Spark</a>.)<br/><br/>It's a bit obsolete now, yeah; like a lot of new mechanics, they overcosted it.  8 mana for 3 damage a turn was a bit much even at the time.  But it was a very important card in its day, not so much because of its raw power but because it was doing something that people hadn't really seen before and opened up new areas of design as a result.<br/><br/>(The fact that it was really fun to use in casual didn't hurt, of course.)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '315906'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy93120\">Aquillion</span>\r\n                                (5/13/2013 11:14:40 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u